<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styleindex.css"/> 
    
    <title>CodeBusters</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
   <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <a class="navbar-brand logo" href="/"><b>CodeBusters</b></a>
  </div>
</nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container main-content-area">
        <div class="row w-100 align-items-center justify-content-center">
            
            <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-md-flex justify-content-center">
                <img src="your-mascot.png" alt="CodeBusters" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 400px;" />
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center text-center text-md-start">
                
                <h1 class="display-5 mb-4">Забавният и ефективен начин да се научите да програмирате!</h1>
                
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-10 col-sm-8 col-md-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
                    
                    <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-lg btn-custom btn-register">Регистрация</a>
                    
                    <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-lg btn-custom btn-login">Вход в профил</a>
                    
                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-custom btn-guest" id="guestBtn" >Играй като гост</button>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer fixed-bottom">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p class="m-0">&copy; Направено от Камен и Георги най-добрите програмисти</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <script>
        document.getElementById('guestBtn').addEventListener('click', () => {
            window.location.href = '/main?guest=true';  
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>